{"title": "Fail-Slow at Scale: Evidence of Hardware Performance Faults in Large Production Systems.", "fields": ["jitter", "computer hardware", "failure mode and effects analysis", "real time computing", "computer science", "operator"], "abstract": "Fail-slow hardware is an under-studied failure mode. We present a study of 114 reports of fail-slow hardware incidents, collected from large-scale cluster deployments in 14 institutions. We show that all hardware types such as disk, SSD, CPU, memory, and network components can exhibit performance faults. We made several important observations such as faults convert from one form to another, the cascading root causes and impacts can be long, and fail-slow faults can have varying symptoms. From this study, we make suggestions to vendors, operators, and systems designers.", "citation": "Not cited", "departments": ["University of Chicago", "University of Chicago", "Pure Storage", "Pure Storage", "Parallel Machines"], "authors": ["Haryadi S. Gunawi.....http://dblp.org/pers/hd/g/Gunawi:Haryadi_S=", "Riza O. Suminto.....http://dblp.org/pers/hd/s/Suminto:Riza_O=", "Russell Sears.....http://dblp.org/pers/hd/s/Sears:Russell", "Casey Golliher.....http://dblp.org/pers/hd/g/Golliher:Casey", "Swaminathan Sundararaman.....http://dblp.org/pers/hd/s/Sundararaman:Swaminathan", "Xing Lin.....http://dblp.org/pers/hd/l/Lin:Xing", "Tim Emami.....http://dblp.org/pers/hd/e/Emami:Tim", "Weiguang Sheng.....http://dblp.org/pers/hd/s/Sheng:Weiguang", "Nematollah Bidokhti.....http://dblp.org/pers/hd/b/Bidokhti:Nematollah", "Caitie McCaffrey.....http://dblp.org/pers/hd/m/McCaffrey:Caitie", "Gary Grider.....http://dblp.org/pers/hd/g/Grider:Gary", "Parks M. Fields.....http://dblp.org/pers/hd/f/Fields:Parks_M=", "Kevin Harms.....http://dblp.org/pers/hd/h/Harms:Kevin", "Robert B. Ross.....http://dblp.org/pers/hd/r/Ross:Robert_B=", "Andree Jacobson.....http://dblp.org/pers/hd/j/Jacobson:Andree", "Robert Ricci.....http://dblp.org/pers/hd/r/Ricci:Robert", "